    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《占领火星：序章》</strong> 作为体验版，完全免费。快去体验火星探索的旅程吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这个游戏版本是2020年的，不代表当前完整版本！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>For the current build play Occupy Mars: The Game not Prologue !</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310520/extras/edb0161b9db9f6489684d466613502c3.webp?t=1753711660\" width=616 height=1 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《占领火星》是一款有关火星探索的充满科技感的开放世界沙盒生存游戏。游戏的灵感来源于人类渴望探索地外世界的美好愿景，及当下地外探索的众多科技发展成果。在游戏里，你可以进行升级基地，探索未至之境，在火星上进行矿物挖掘，作物生产，化学实验等生存行为。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310520/extras/3a19182c1449dc1a979f164ce3bd2213.poster.avif?t=1753711660\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310520/extras/3a19182c1449dc1a979f164ce3bd2213.webm?t=1753711660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310520/extras/3a19182c1449dc1a979f164ce3bd2213.mp4?t=1753711660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >序章部分发生在火星的一处偏僻之隅，且整个故事发生在本体的时间线之前。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为第一批成功登上火星的探索者，你被派往盖尔陨石坑中的远程研究中心执行任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310520/extras/921174764df714c9013f58bc34885d19.poster.avif?t=1753711660\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310520/extras/921174764df714c9013f58bc34885d19.webm?t=1753711660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310520/extras/921174764df714c9013f58bc34885d19.mp4?t=1753711660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的任务就是收集数据和资源。但你得手脚麻利点，因为沙尘暴很快就要来临，但你手上的水和食物已经所剩无几。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310520/extras/0cbaec163d4a21460f94849e62173e5b.poster.avif?t=1753711660\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310520/extras/0cbaec163d4a21460f94849e62173e5b.webm?t=1753711660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310520/extras/0cbaec163d4a21460f94849e62173e5b.mp4?t=1753711660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要谨慎思考，大胆行事……风暴来袭，你，是否能够逃出生天？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310520/extras/c0dfa7923362d8110f3740db728ac937.poster.avif?t=1753711660\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310520/extras/c0dfa7923362d8110f3740db728ac937.webm?t=1753711660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310520/extras/c0dfa7923362d8110f3740db728ac937.mp4?t=1753711660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
